commit message: Fixed SSL problems (Issue #233) by adding more of the disabled cipher suites
Fixed download of attached media files (Issue #256) by trying to guess the filename from the URL in a better way.
Enable SSL- and HTTP-Auth-Preferences to be specified per Wifi network too (Issue #261)

== Version 1.78 ==
* Enable API-Level 21 (Lollipop, 5.0)
* Fixed several bugs regarding the improved TLS-security (Issue #233)
* Enable SSL- and HTTP-Auth-Preferences to be specified per Wifi network too (Issue #261)
* Fixed download of attached media files (Issue #256)
